The Americans have a new "smart weapon"
The US army has sent a new "smart" weapon to Afghanistan, known only as XM-25.
The generals believe that this new automatic rifle will have an influence on the conflict there with the Taliban and "will change the game" for their benefit.
The new weapon is like a super accurate cannon.
Its projectiles are laser guided with a precision of a few meters.
The special 25 mm calibre ammunition developed for this rifle and containing a highly shattering explosive, actually works like small grenades.
Ammunition can be programmed in such a way that it will explode in contact with the target and at any point in its ballistic trajectory.
