One source, he said, "explained that business owners in Moscow understood that it was better to obtain the protection of the MVD and FSB (rather than organized crime groups) because they not only have more weapons, more means and more power than criminal groups but are also protected by law."
"This is why the demand for protection by criminal gangs is no longer so high."
